                    <span>I must say I'm not very programming-savvy, but I'm only through the first 1/3 of the book and am very impressed-- the scripting content is so thorough and packed... the author really knows this stuff! There's so much ground covered here I think this is the ultimate game scripting bible and a must have, esp for the beginner. Excellent job!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A HULK of a scripting book</div>
